Thats what, I do hehe and you needed to look in the CommunityResourcePack folder and then open CommonResources.cfg and in the list you will found 

    RESOURCE_DEFINITION{	name = Karbonite	density = 0.0125	[COLOR="#FF0000"]unitCost = 100.6[/COLOR]      // And , I have it set at 100.6 you can change it to what ever.	flowMode = STAGE_PRIORITY_FLOW 	transfer = PUMP	isTweakable = true}

EDIT- If you want a MM Patch maybe something like 

    @RESOURCE_DEFINITION[Karbonite]{	@name = Karbonite	%unitCost = 100.6 }

